PwC goes to Anggrek Campus!
 
"Were calling all fourth year students and fresh graduates to join this event. Lets discover endless opportunities at PwC Indonesia.
 
Join us for ON-SITE PwC campus hiring and get ready to kick-start your career with PwC Indonesia!
Mark and save the date:
 
 14 MARET 2023
 09.00  11.00
 Kampus Anggrek, Faculty Lounge 8th floor
 Register via link bit.ly/PwC_CampusHiringBINUS or scan the QR code by Thursday, 9 March 2023 at the latest

We cant wait to see you!

Samsung Research Indonesia in collaboration with BINUS Career presents
WORKSHOP & CAMPUS HIRING
For Global Software Engineer
 
Good news for all Binusian!
 
Whos excited to be the part of Samsung Research Indonesia team? This March, we invite you to join this most-waited hiring event from Samsung Research Indonesia (SRIN)!
 
Join the seminar and recruitment test ON-SITE at Kampus Anggrek-BINUS University! On this event therell be 2 agenda:
 Workshop
for all students & alumni (preferably from Computer Science/related major)

 Technical Test
for last semester students and alumni from Computer Science/related major

Mark your calendar!
 15 MARET 2023
 09.00  finish
 ON-SITE at BINUS University, Kampus Anggrek
 Workshop: Hall 8th Floor (Aula Lnt. 8 / Ruang 800)
 Technical Test: Room 810
 Register via link: https://bit.ly/seminar-recruitmentSRIN2023

Get yourself ready, and see you there!

For more information go to: https://www.samsung.com/id/srin/

Selamat kepada Anastasya Anirudha (2401960725) yang berhasil menjadi Juara 2 Lomba UI/UX Paras ICT VIII yang diadakan oleh Institur Bisnis dan Teknologi Indonesia.

Hi Binusian
 
Ingin mahir di bidang karir impianmu?
Binus Career hadir mengadakan Webinar dengan tema "Mahir Karir Bareng Binus Career" secara hybrid lho!

Pada acara webinar kali ini akan ada:

 Opening speech dari Prof.DR.Meyliana, S.Kom., M.M., CDMS, CBDMP yang merupakan Vice Rector Global Employability & Entrepreneurship
 Pembicara dari Dr. Ratna Sari, S.Kom., M.Msi yang merupakan BINUS Career Manager

Acara Webinar ini akan dilaksanakan pada:
Hari / Tanggal : Sabtu, 4 Maret 2023
Pukul : 10.00 WIB s/d selesai
Tempat : Zoom Meeting & Kampus Syahdan Ruangan M2CD

Registrasi sekarang 
https://bit.ly/MahirCareerBarengBINUSCareer

Selain kamu akan mendapatkan banyak insight baru, bagi para peserta yang hadir onsite akan mendapatkan bingkisan menarik. Dengan mengikuti acara ini kalian akan mendapatkan Point SAT & E-Certificate, lho!

Tunggu apalagi, yuk langsung aja daftar karena ini limited seat!
Terima Kasih, sampai ketemu!
